{"tid":596205,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【娶日本老婆最幸福？】日本男性遭家暴人數 4年增4倍","createTime":"2018-03-17T11:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T12:33:35.000Z","uid":122,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"27b0836a19c08a3ae8bfd3b6347b2c872f45d7f0","tid":596205,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:45:56.000Z","msg":"日本去年發生7.24萬宗家暴案，女性受害人佔82.8%，大幅高於男性的17.2%。雖然女性遭受家暴比男性普遍，但日本男性遭家暴的人數，過去4年其實激增了4倍。<br />\n<br />\n據警方掌握的數字，去年的家暴案件比之前一年增加3.6%，亦是連續第14年上升。警方以暴力和傷害等罪名立案調查的案件，連續2年超過8000宗，刷新歷史紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n去年遭家暴的日本男性，有1.24萬人，比2013年時的3281人，增加近4倍。警方認為主要因為人們提高對家暴的認識，遇事時會報警有關。<br />\n<br />\n從年齡來看，施暴者以30歲和40歲組群最多，分別佔27.9%和26.3%。而受害人以30多歲的人最多，佔28.8%。"},{"pid":"0a13996217ecb9d36db76f8ab4e5b4b3f36564d9","tid":596205,"uid":86097,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:49:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3274e520bdc8bd7cdf33ec0bbaedd8d7a8680636","tid":596205,"uid":122,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:50:29.000Z","msg":"快點家暴我"},{"pid":"a4d871f83c10c59d88b6c3d91962e9871fd00827","tid":596205,"uid":3818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:55:38.000Z","msg":"好想比架妹用粗口侮辱我 再用腳踏我個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b1ab170112dbd519bc571a5a8ee3b460a4d32f2","tid":596205,"uid":9231,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T12:00:52.000Z","msg":"我條女成日用對奶塞我塊面<br />\n成日抖唔到氣 差D死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/200035_38e85a8331b853b890c1a5034d21170d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F200035_38e85a8331b853b890c1a5034d21170d.jpg&h=291be3c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">示意圖</span>"},{"pid":"fc263c3d62da489026cb1707555fce9368716fac","tid":596205,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":